results.name: Multiply, cell by cell, the sequences A096162, A048996 and A178886.
comment: Shape sequence for this irregular table is A000041.
example: Row 3: (1,1,6) times (1,2,1) times (2,2,1) yielding (2,4,6) with row sum 12 agreeing with 1,3,12,60,360,...; cf. A001700.
